Summary: 
 * BIG MERGE FROM SysteMoC--mainline--0.8
 - merged *_entry_base with *_entry classes and *_outlet_base
   with *_outlet classes (derive again directly from smoc_chan_{in,out}_if)
 - added moreData(), lessData(), moreSpace() and lessSpace()
   methods to smoc_chan_{in,out}_if, this may be used to unify
   entry, outlet <-> channel communication
 - smoc_multireader_chan: moved EventMap to Outlets; use unified
   interface described above
 - smoc_multicase_sr_signal_chan: use unified interface described
   above
 - commented out debug statements in smoc_multiplex_fifo.hpp
 - Fixed multiplex fifos (hopefully)
 - SGX-Graph generation: Dump native WSDF edge parameters
 - Allow to store WSDF edge parameters into stream
 - Allow to read back WSDF edge parameters
 - Dummy commit because last patch description has not been complete
 - Move some functionality into libWSDF
 - multiplex fifo fixes

